# Stage: integrate — merge + tag + deploy (or simulate)

## Goal

Produce a structured `integration-log.json` that records what would be
done to merge the verified+reviewed patch into the target branch. AISEP
does NOT auto-execute git/deploy commands in v0; this stage produces the
*plan* for the human (or future automated integrate executor) to apply.

This is the **G-i / IOC anchor** equivalent — the last machine gate
before the change reaches the target system.

